ing: 1 pound boneless chicken breast halves, cooked and diced
des: "Savory and tasty, a great recipe to make.  Just throw everything in the slow cooker on your way out the door in the morning, and a delicious soup will greet you on your return.  The whole family will like this down to home soup."
ins: Combine celery, chicken pieces, chicken broth, water, mixed vegetables, rice, parsley and herb seasoning in a slow cooker.  Cover, and cook on low 6 to 8 hours.   If soup is too thick, add more water to dilute and allow 15 minutes of additional cooking time.
